---
title: Chicken Noodle Laksa with Coconut-Curry Broth
description: 'Laksa' is a creamy coconut-based noodle soup popular in Malaysian cuisine! Lemongrass- spiced chicken and hearty noodles are the perfect pairings for this delicious broth - we guarantee you'll be slurping this up in record time.
